      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:2:1:136:11",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) اتَّقُوا الظُّلْمَ فَإِنَّهُ ظُلُمَاتُ يَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Mansour, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘Fear the injustice for it would be a darkness on the Day of Judgment’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "11. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from Mansur from Hisham ibn Salim from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “The Messenger of Allah has said, ‘Be afraid of doing injustice; on the Day of Judgment there will be much darkness.’” "
        ]
      }
